@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

# =============================================================
# Users
# =============================================================

### [Users] 一覧取得
GET {{baseUrl}}/

###

### [Users] Create → 201 Created + 作成したユーザーのJSON
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice",
  "email": "alice@example.com"
}

###

### [Users] Update → 200 OK (idはクエリパラメータ)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/update?id=20
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice Updated",
  "icon_url": "https://example.com/icon.png"
}

###

### [Users] Delete → 200 OK (idはクエリパラメータ)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/delete?id=20

# =============================================================
# Tabs
# =============================================================

###

### [Tabs] 一覧取得
GET {{baseUrl}}/tabs

###

### [Tabs] Create → 201 Created + 作成したタブのJSON (user_idは実際の値に変更)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tabs/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": 1,
  "title": "Wonderwall",
  "content": "Capo 2\nEm G D A"
}

###

### [Tabs] Update → 200 OK (idはクエリパラメータ)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tabs/update?id=30
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Wonderwall (Updated)",
  "content": "Capo 2\nEm G D A\nUpdated content"
}

###

### [Tabs] Delete → 200 OK (idはクエリパラメータ)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tabs/delete?id=30
